org.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM spree_products INNER JOIN spree_product_properties ON spree_product_properties.product_id = spree_products.id INNER JOIN spree_properties ON spree_properties.id = spree_product_properties.property_id WHERE spree_products.deleted_at IS NULL AND spree_product_properties.value = 'fake' AND spree_properties.id = "$1"
